QatarEnergy LNG — Financial Model
A group - project Financial model built in Excel analyzing the viability of a large-scale LNG development. The model covers a multi-year loan schedule, monthly and annual cash budgets, and revenue and cost timing assumptions including interest capitalization during construction, revenue lag, COGS mechanics, and crew salary structuring.
Built as part of BUSI 414 - Financial Modelling.

